Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.02,0:00:07.15,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,It was a small incident that happened to me, Nanoha Takamachi,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.15,0:00:10.61,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,a girl who was supposed to be an ordinary third-grader.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.26,0:00:15.79,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,I believed in the courage within my heart,\Nand I gained magical powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.73,0:00:20.17,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,I wished for a very small feeling to reach its destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.07,0:00:25.04,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,The beginning of the journey must always be so sad,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.04,0:00:28.37,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,but I'm sure the feelings have gotten across.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.38,0:00:33.61,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,So I'm sure {\i0}goodbye{\i1} is the word that begins something.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.55,0:00:38.75,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,{\i0}Magical Girl Lyrical Nanoha{\i1}\Nwill now begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.72,0:01:00.66,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,Cradling my knees in a corner of my room
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.66,0:01:04.19,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,I always shivered from uncertainty
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.19,0:01:11.23,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,I was scared of learning the truth,\Nso I closed the door
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.23,0:01:18.57,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,I found my own place within a kind lie and I fled inside my dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.57,0:01:27.15,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,I dye a sea of loneliness that nobody knows of into a deep blue
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.15,0:01:32.92,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,An intense feeling to hide the loneliness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.92,0:01:39.19,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,Is continually injuring your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.19,0:01:43.87,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,The secret hidden deep within the eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.87,0:01:48.40,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,To the truth behind the smile that draws me in
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.40,0:01:53.84,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,I will deliver a love so soft
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.84,0:01:58.38,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,Right now, a warmth that might break upon touching it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.38,0:02:02.95,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,Parts itself from the past, and overflows
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.95,0:02:07.52,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,I'll be by your side forever
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.52,0:02:17.52,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,Do not be lured into the somber shadows
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.06,0:02:31.79,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Please, everyone!\NHurry up and escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.41,0:02:40.70,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.98,0:02:44.14,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.22,0:02:52.95,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Fate! Fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.76,0:02:58.95,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.06,0:03:04.00,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Fly! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.03,0:03:54.02,Nanoha Title2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(917,0)\an5\pos(480,240)}{\c&HE9C5A0&}Episode 13
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.03,0:03:54.02,Nanoha Title2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(917,0)\an5\pos(480,473)}{\c&HE9C5A0&}Call My Name
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.56,0:04:08.89,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Looks like the earthquake is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.83,0:04:11.06,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.27,0:04:15.90,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,The Garden's destruction is complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.90,0:04:18.51,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Everything has been absorbed into the imaginary number plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.51,0:04:21.84,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,The dimensional tremor is ending.\NThere are no dimensional faults.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.84,0:04:22.91,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.91,0:04:24.55,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Escaping at Speed Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.55,0:04:26.38,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Returning to our patrol course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.52,0:04:35.32,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Where's Fate?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.32,0:04:37.36,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,She's in the brig with Arf.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.36,0:04:40.36,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Since she's a material witness in this incident...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.36,0:04:42.96,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but she will be detained for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.96,0:04:44.93,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,But that's... ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.93,0:04:46.53,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Nanoha, stay still!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.87,0:04:51.44,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,This incident was a major case, where one mistaken step
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.44,0:04:54.91,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,might have caused the creation of a dimensional fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.91,0:04:57.21,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,The Time-Space Administrative Bureau has to be very careful
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.21,0:04:59.88,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,about the treatment of all involved parties.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.88,0:05:01.47,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,You understand that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.02,0:05:03.98,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.98,0:05:05.92,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Amy, do it over!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.92,0:05:06.91,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Darn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.30,0:05:23.13,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,And so, all sorts of things came to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.10,0:05:27.04,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,From the day that I met\NYuuno until today...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.04,0:05:30.21,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Now that everything's over, it seems like it all happened in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.94,0:05:33.58,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,We spent several days aboard the {\i1}Arthra{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.58,0:05:37.38,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,until the aftershocks of the dimensional tremor subsided.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.38,0:05:38.68,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Rice bowl...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.30,0:05:59.03,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Since then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.21,0:06:06.08,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,You demonstrated outstanding service in the resolution of this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.08,0:06:07.98,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Even if it's a bit informal,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.98,0:06:10.61,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'd like to award you for your distinguished service.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.95,0:06:16.69,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Miss Nanoha Takamachi and Mr. Yuuno Scrya,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.29,0:06:19.56,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.01,0:06:39.71,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Chrono, what's going to happen to Fate now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.71,0:06:43.25,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Though she had her reasons, it's an undeniable fact
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.25,0:06:46.62,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,that she was part of a conspiracy in meddling with the dimensions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.76,0:06:49.42,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,That's a felony.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.42,0:06:51.79,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Usually, you get locked up for several centuries, if not more.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.79,0:06:53.09,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,That can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.09,0:06:54.22,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,However!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.56,0:06:59.07,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,The situation is rather special, and it's clear that
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.07,0:07:02.70,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,she wasn't party to the dimensional crimes of her own will.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.64,0:07:08.38,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,What we have left is to figure out
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.38,0:07:11.04,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,how to get the brass to understand those facts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.04,0:07:13.61,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,But I'm pretty confident on that score,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.61,0:07:15.52,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,so you don't have to worry at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.52,0:07:17.18,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Chrono...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.18,0:07:20.02,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,The Time-Space Administrative Bureau isn't a group
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.02,0:07:23.82,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,of cold-hearted people who'd pin a crime on a girl who knew nothing,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.82,0:07:27.26,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,and was just doing her best to grant her mother's wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.40,0:07:34.70,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Chrono... can it be that you're actually a really kind person?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.70,0:07:35.76,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.34,0:07:42.21,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,That was just stating the obvious as an Enforcer!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.21,0:07:44.14,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,There were no personal feelings involved!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.11,0:07:47.28,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,You don't have to be embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.28,0:07:49.08,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'm not embarrassed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.08,0:07:51.75,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,What?! Don't laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.12,0:07:56.29,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,The dimensional tremor aftershocks will be subsiding soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.29,0:08:01.06,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I think we can get back to your world by tomorrow, Miss Nanoha.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.33,0:08:02.70,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.70,0:08:07.57,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,However, the route to Midchilda hasn't stabilized quite yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.57,0:08:09.80,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,It looks like that will take some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.80,0:08:11.17,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.17,0:08:13.44,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,A few months, maybe half a year...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.44,0:08:17.58,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,It looks like it will take that long before we can cruise safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.58,0:08:19.21,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.21,0:08:21.55,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Well, my clan is full of people
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.55,0:08:24.82,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,who wander all over the world in search of archaeological ruins,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.82,0:08:28.36,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,so there really isn't a definite necessity for me to hurry back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.36,0:08:32.43,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,But I can't really have you host me on this ship for that long...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.43,0:08:36.13,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Then you can stay at my house, like you have been!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.13,0:08:37.46,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Is that all right, Nanoha?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.46,0:08:38.43,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.43,0:08:40.23,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,As long as you're fine with it, Yuuno.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.23,0:08:41.47,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Then, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.47,0:08:44.47,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Um, please take good care of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.47,0:08:45.50,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.48,0:08:50.61,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Geez, it's because you slept so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.61,0:08:53.58,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,But I was pulling so many all-nighters!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.58,0:08:55.07,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'm still sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.48,0:09:00.12,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,The place called Alhazred that she was aiming for...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.12,0:09:01.82,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,You know of it, right, Yuuno?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.82,0:09:04.26,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yes, I've heard of it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.26,0:09:07.90,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,They say it existed in previous centuries, by the old calendar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.90,0:09:12.40,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,The land where many spells that have been lost now still rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.40,0:09:13.43,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,But they also say
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.43,0:09:17.24,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,that it fell into a dimensional fault long ago and fell to ruins.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.24,0:09:18.54,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Hey there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.31,0:09:22.74,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,They say that there is no wish you can leave ungranted
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.74,0:09:26.88,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,using the powers of the secret spells of Alhazred,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.88,0:09:29.32,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,with all sorts of magic in its ultimate state.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.32,0:09:34.28,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Magic that can turn back time and space, and even rewrite the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.82,0:09:38.46,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Magic that can bring back to the living a life that has been lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.46,0:09:40.43,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Those were the things she wanted, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.43,0:09:41.40,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.40,0:09:45.17,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,But everyone who learns magic knows for a fact
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.17,0:09:49.67,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,that turning back time and raising the dead is impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.67,0:09:52.57,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,That is why, seeking both of those ideals,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.57,0:09:56.28,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,she could only rely on such a fairy-tale legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.28,0:09:58.35,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,She had no choice but to rely on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.35,0:10:03.55,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,But a mage of that level was risking her life in that search.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.55,0:10:09.29,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Perhaps she really had found the path to Alhazred.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.96,0:10:12.32,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Though there's no way for us to know now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.60,0:10:21.40,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, this mealtime story has gotten quite long.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.40,0:10:23.24,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Let's finish our meals before they get cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.24,0:10:27.57,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'm sure this will be your last meal aboard the {\i1}Arthra{\i0}, Nanoha.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.57,0:10:28.51,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.51,0:10:30.38,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,If parting ways makes you lonely,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.38,0:10:32.95,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,you should honestly just come out and say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.95,0:10:34.98,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Chrono, you're so shy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.98,0:10:36.28,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.28,0:10:40.29,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Nanoha, you can always come by and visit us, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.29,0:10:42.29,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yes! Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.29,0:10:45.73,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Amy! The {\i1}Arthra{\i0} is not a playground!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.73,0:10:47.89,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Well now, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.89,0:10:51.43,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,When our mission is to patrol, we're always full of idle time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.43,0:10:53.66,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Ca... Captain! You as well?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.54,0:10:59.34,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,And the morning where Yuuno and I were going home...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.41,0:11:03.44,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Well... thank you so much for everything you did this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.44,0:11:05.24,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,We appreciated your support.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.89,0:11:15.06,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'll inform you of Fate's treatment when it's been decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.06,0:11:18.26,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,It's all right, I'll make sure that nothing bad happens to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.26,0:11:20.43,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yeah... thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.43,0:11:24.00,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yuuno, when you want to go back, please contact us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.00,0:11:25.57,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'll let you use our gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.57,0:11:27.83,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yes! Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.77,0:11:31.41,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Then, I guess we're about ready to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.41,0:11:32.97,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.97,0:11:34.03,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.41,0:11:39.51,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'll see you again, Chrono,\NMiss Amy, Miss Lindy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.36,0:11:58.87,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Should we go home now, Yuuno?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.87,0:11:59.99,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.34,0:12:09.71,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.55,0:12:13.88,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Nanoha!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.88,0:12:17.28,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,And what comes back is my everyday life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.42,0:12:19.89,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,It's the same as it had always been,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.89,0:12:21.72,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,but adding everything that has happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.79,0:12:22.99,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Mom, I'm hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.72,0:12:24.62,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,everyday life is just a little bit different from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.66,0:12:26.72,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.06,0:12:29.50,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Were you a good girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.50,0:12:30.46,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.64,0:12:37.70,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Nanoha!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.70,0:12:38.93,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,{\c&HE1E1E1&}Nanoha!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.61,0:12:45.37,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'm home! I came back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.48,0:12:51.35,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,The time that you're engrossed in something,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.35,0:12:55.31,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,after it's all over, seems like a fleeting moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.96,0:13:05.49,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,But in my heart, it surely remains true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.40,0:13:10.86,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,How we met... how desperate I was... all sorts of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.39,0:13:27.62,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,It's been a while since I slept in my own bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.62,0:13:30.49,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yuuno, you should rest up tonight too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.49,0:13:31.69,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.69,0:13:34.63,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Thanks for all the hard work,\NRaising Heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.65,0:13:54.74,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Thank you for all the hard work, Nanoha.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.92,0:14:06.38,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,The one thing that's still on my mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.49,0:14:11.52,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,About that girl with the gentle eyes, that must surely be very kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.48,0:14:27.74,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Several days later...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.02,0:14:53.55,Nanoha Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\an5\frz6.941\pos(439,167)}{\fs37.5\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}Incoming Call
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.02,0:14:53.55,Nanoha Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\an5\frz7.41\pos(478.667,383)}{\fs32\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}Time-Space\NAdministrative Bureau
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.61,0:14:56.44,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is Nanoha!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.81,0:15:01.92,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.92,0:15:04.52,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's been officially decided on a few moments ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.52,0:15:07.25,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Fate will be transferred over to the Main Office,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.25,0:15:10.52,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,and there she will face questioning and a trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.52,0:15:15.16,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Fate will probably—no, almost definitely—be acquitted.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.16,0:15:16.23,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Everything will be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.23,0:15:19.83,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Because Chrono was working overtime to gather all the evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.83,0:15:23.57,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Amy! You don't have to mention unnecessary information like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.57,0:15:25.51,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Chrono!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.74,0:15:31.21,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,The questioning, trial, and everything else will take quite a bit of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.21,0:15:32.81,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,But, before that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.81,0:15:33.85,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.85,0:15:35.15,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.15,0:15:36.92,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'll be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.92,0:15:37.98,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.05,0:15:40.54,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,What's up, Nanoha?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.59,0:15:45.56,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Fate is going to be transferred to the Main Office for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.56,0:15:49.33,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,But before that, I can see her for just a little bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.33,0:15:50.56,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.56,0:15:53.26,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,She's saying that she wants to see me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.96,0:16:22.05,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.57,0:16:36.04,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,We don't have much time, but sit down and have a talk for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.04,0:16:37.74,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,We'll be over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.61,0:16:39.67,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.31,0:16:42.58,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.01,0:17:14.15,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,There were so many things\NI wanted to talk to you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.15,0:17:15.68,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,But it's funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.68,0:17:19.22,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,When I saw your face, Fate,\NI forgot all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.22,0:17:22.86,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I... let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.86,0:17:25.35,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I can't put it into words well, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.03,0:17:28.69,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,But I was really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.20,0:17:32.26,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,That you looked at me so straightforwardly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.83,0:17:36.79,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I thought that it would be great if we could be friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.74,0:17:41.67,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,But today, you have to head out right after this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.44,0:17:46.97,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,That's true. It will be a pretty long trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.95,0:17:49.68,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,But I can see you again, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.09,0:17:59.79,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,It's a bit sad, but I can finally begin to be my own self.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.69,0:18:04.66,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I had you come here so that\NI could give you an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.33,0:18:13.01,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,The words that you told me...\NThat you wanted to be my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.01,0:18:14.41,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.41,0:18:17.74,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,If it's possible for me... if you're okay with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.41,0:18:21.75,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,But I don't know what I should be doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.35,0:18:24.32,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,So I want you to tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.32,0:18:26.68,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,How do you become a friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.40,0:18:36.92,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,That's easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.16,0:18:40.93,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,It's really easy to become friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.94,0:18:45.70,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Call me by my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.07,0:18:49.28,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,In the beginning, that's all you have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.28,0:18:52.38,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Not "you" or "hey, you" or anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.38,0:18:54.18,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Look directly at the person's eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.18,0:18:56.71,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,and clearly call them by their name.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.12,0:19:00.75,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'm Nanoha Takamachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.75,0:19:01.85,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Call me Nanoha!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.89,0:19:04.19,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Nanoha...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.19,0:19:05.85,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yeah! That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.03,0:19:08.86,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Nanoha...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.86,0:19:10.06,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.16,0:19:12.33,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Nanoha!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.30,0:19:14.46,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.74,0:19:21.77,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Nanoha.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.74,0:19:24.07,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.11,0:19:26.41,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Nanoha...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.45,0:19:32.48,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.15,0:19:37.28,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Your hands are so warm, Nanoha.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.96,0:19:45.86,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,There's something that I figured out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.87,0:19:51.10,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,When a friend is crying, you're sad in the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.97,0:19:53.53,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.81,0:19:56.94,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Nanoha.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.94,0:20:00.55,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,We'll part for now, but I'm sure we'll see each other again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.55,0:20:04.85,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,When that happens, can I call you by your name again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.85,0:20:06.98,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.89,0:20:10.79,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,When I want to see you,\NI'm sure to be calling your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.19,0:20:15.96,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,So Nanoha, I want you to call for me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.40,0:20:19.83,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,If something is troubling you, Nanoha...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.83,0:20:23.43,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that this time,\NI will save you, Nanoha.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.08,0:20:39.42,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Your girl over there...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.42,0:20:40.95,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Nanoha...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.95,0:20:43.29,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,She sure is a good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.29,0:20:46.59,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Fate is smiling so much right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.30,0:21:00.47,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,It's time. Are you about done?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.91,0:21:04.24,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.12,0:21:16.36,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,This is all I have that I can use as a token of our memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.36,0:21:18.12,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Then, I should too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.87,0:21:30.89,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Nanoha.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.87,0:21:33.20,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Fate...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.51,0:21:36.34,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'm sure once again...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.34,0:21:38.44,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I'm sure once again...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.52,0:21:45.52,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.52,0:21:47.51,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Miss Arf, you stay well too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.15,0:21:51.12,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Thanks for everything,\NNanoha, Yuuno.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.12,0:21:53.03,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Well then, I'm on my way too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.03,0:21:54.56,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,See you later, Chrono!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.56,0:21:55.65,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.61,0:22:13.88,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye, see you later...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.28,0:22:16.87,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Chrono...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.88,0:22:19.97,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Miss Arf...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.45,0:22:23.85,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.16,0:23:07.46,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Nanoha?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.20,0:23:11.19,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.56,0:23:14.13,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,Make a little wish
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.13,0:23:19.63,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,Even though at times\NI'll trip or get lost
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.07,0:23:30.07,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,Because you're with me, I can continue to smile and be energetic
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.32,0:23:42.06,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,Ah, don't look down\Nas you walk, it's all right
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.06,0:23:49.64,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,The courage that you handed to me that day is still in my hands
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.77,0:23:46.97,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Nanoha!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.33,0:23:49.64,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.64,0:23:57.01,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,Each time I blink,\Nmore kindness is born
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.01,0:24:05.25,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,See, this love is something I want to nurture always, forever
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.25,0:24:07.09,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,Make a little wish
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.09,0:24:13.03,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,Wearing the lemon-colored\Ndrops from the moon
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.03,0:24:20.03,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,I want to keep glimmering with a twinkle and keep on as your energy
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.03,0:24:21.47,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,Make a little wish
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.47,0:24:27.37,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,On rainy days and dawns\Nwhen I couldn't fall asleep
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.37,0:24:34.41,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,Because you were here with me,\NI was able to smile my best
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.41,0:24:38.11,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,Just like this
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.39,0:24:49.60,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,Whenever we're apart, I still have something I can believe in
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.60,0:24:58.14,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,See, our hearts are always,\Nsurely together as one
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.14,0:24:59.67,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,Make a little wish
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.67,0:25:05.55,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,Collecting the lemon-colored\Ndrops from the moon
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.55,0:25:12.62,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,Let's turn them into warm tears, and make them spices for smiles
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.62,0:25:14.22,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,Make a little wish
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.22,0:25:20.09,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,Even though at times\NI'll trip or get lost
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.09,0:25:30.09,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,Because you're with me, I can continue to smile and be energetic
